  "title": "Our Year-end Thoughts",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael, Sarah, Gladys and Mark discuss what is top of mind as we draw to the end of 2023. Topics include what work we've done over the year, as well as items from Ignite.\n                  There's also a discsussion of EQ and IQ and a different sign-off! See you all in 2024!\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1270426?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1270426/\">EoY2023</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1270426/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.microsoft.com/ignite-2023-book-of-news/\">Microsoft Ignite Book of News</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://codeql.github.com/\">CodeQL</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2312.02119.pdf\">Tree of Attacks: Jailbreaking Black-Box LLMs Automatically</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Designing-Developing-Solutions-Developer-Practices-ebook/dp/B0BFXG89B6/\">Designing and Developing Secure Azure Solutions (Developer Best Practices)</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Microsoft-Azure-Security-Grundprinzipien-Anwendungen-ebook/dp/B0CLKZLS1F\">Microsoft Azure Security: Bewährte Methoden, Prozesse und Grundprinzi